472
00:39:23,175 --> 00:39:24,654
- I am?
- Very.

473
00:39:25,535 --> 00:39:29,085
Your friend just bought you
a lap dance with me.

474
00:39:31,577 --> 00:39:35,695
- Excuse me?
- So where you from, David?

475
00:39:36,618 --> 00:39:40,611
